&lt;p&gt;Updated this file with: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=rev&amp;amp;revision=476964&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=rev&amp;amp;revision=476964&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;M    java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/master/j9_13/updatableResultSet.out&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that with 10.2, this test is skipped with this jvm.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
